le="text-align: center;"><span style="color:#ffffff;">Testimonials</span></h5>
</div></div></div><div id="a191f1affe6303d4ca29e18b172bea0e" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-horizontal"><div id="a191f3e85eef00d6a7102ec23a943753" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a191f1affe6305e98e314f1f41a3e002" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div><div id="a191f1affe6306daf3ca372cfc291ad7" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom8" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:12px;">Jyothi joined us 2 years ago. Under her leadership, the engineering department had several accomplishments. She either introduced new or streamlined existing processes, expedited feature development, brought in technology innovation including the unified platform initiative, and reduced cost.  Her contributions are immensely appreciated - CFO</span></p>
</div><div id="a191f29ad1ab009f39da0abfe0ac5e27" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="item "><div id="a191f1affe6307eaa0203e0c426b2917" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a191f1affe630833124175b0da853e78" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-horizontal"><div id="a191f2ad334300a4cea7dc0c4f3ffef7" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a191f2a1c56f00f45913f1672142bfeb" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h5 class="wb-stl-subtitle" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color:#ffffff;">Testimonials</span></h5>
</div></div></div><div id="a191f1affe6309e8bbd8301b07a93f09" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a191f1affe630bae2ed910209587d62f" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div><div id="a191f1affe630c307c803d84908b51dd" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom8" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:12px;">Jyothi is a seasoned professional who knows her craft very well. I've worked with her on many projects and have witnessed first hand her ability to organize people and implement processes. She's very persuasive and is able to breakdown technical Dev Ops procedures into consumable chunks to the team. One of my favorite traits about Jyothi is that she always has documentation around her objectives and processes. I've collaborated with her on many projects and have always been impressed with how much substance she brought to the table with respect to QE and DevOps procedures. She was a joy to work with and I strongly recommend her for a leadership role - VP, Customer Experience</span></p>
</div><div id="a191f29b0e7e005c2eab51d292a624ce" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="item "><div id="a191f1affe630de0777d15ff630ab531" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a191f1affe630eeb9039ea4f013e776b" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a191f2a3e86c00b938e9e52b9d29f69c" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h5 class="wb-stl-subtitle" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color:#ffffff;">Testimonials</span></h5>
</div><div id="a191f1affe630f92a1e71c1b9e296c0e" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a191f1affe6311d037a67133d0e421e4" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div><div id="a191f1affe6312b78037db4c1aab95fb" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom8" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:12px;">I've had the opportunity to work with Jyothi, where I was consistently impressed with her diligence and ability to get things done. She brought many efficiencies with regards to delivering our product through managing the DevOps and Release Management process. Jyothi will not take a "no" for answer, she will look for other ways and is restless until she can see the results she's looking for. Her drive and hunger to learn and solve problems will continue to be the key to her success. - COO</span></p>
</div><div id="a191f29b6d650093f9d8be3e8df4341f" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="item "><div id="a191f1bd5539003009695555762668f3" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a191f1bd55410009ca7df88a40148511" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a191f2a4bee40043fd08ee2efb175d5c" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h5 class="wb-stl-subtitle" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color:#ffffff;">Testimonials</span></h5>
</div><div id="a191f1bd554900c6f4a8f34adc846231" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a191f1bd555b0067d38f93353f7f723d" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div><div id="a191f1bd5566003b6435840292368f7f" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom6" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:12px;">Jyothi is a brilliant leader to work with. She thinks on the cutting edge of IT leadership, software methodologies, and strategies. Her experience makes her an insightful and independent leader, and the success she achieved while we worked together required extensive knowledge and dedication. She is capable of taking a company technology to a professional, enterprise level. And to top it off, she is a transparent and loyal person to work with. Definitely someone I’d recommend for any leadership position. - IT Manager</span></p>
