</div><div id="a19202e02f430091f371f553280da137" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="a18ab4ff50c92f66f46b16319f0873a9" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><a name="History" class="wb_anchor"></a><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18ab4ff50c930bf9fc88f19a5fe333f" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h5 class="wb-stl-subtitle"><span style="color:#ffffff;">About</span></h5>
</div><div id="a18ab4ff50c93106654c6b34201c1e24" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-size:18px;">Founded in 2024 (Woman-Owned), this is just the beginning of my journey, but the roots run deep. With over 30 years of experience in the industry, I have held pivotal roles at renowned organizations like NASA, eBay, and Pelco by Schneider Electric, and many startups. This wealth of expertise fuels the mission: Aspire, Assess, Act, and Achieve!</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-size:18px;">"Make A Stride" is built on a foundation of excellence, innovation, and a passion for driving transformative change. I can help organizations assess their potential, take decisive action, and achieve lasting success, empowering them to navigate the digital landscape with confidence.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-size:18px;">I am committed to delivering value and making a significant impact across industries.</span></span></p>
